			<h1>Autism services<br> by <span class='uppercase'>Bayada</span> Habilitation</h1>
			<h2 class="italics">Improving the lives of children and adults with autism</h2>
			<div class="widget-story" role="article">
			<figure class="about-main">
				<img src="/images/stories-sidebar/sonny-stories-sidebar.jpg" alt="Bayada client Adam with his nurse Brandi" width="227" height="281">
				<figcaption>Sonny S., who has cerebral palsy, uses his communication device with the help of his <span class='uppercase'>Bayada</span> Hab Tech Megan Barbee.</figcaption>
